{"tid":656722,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[有角色復活?!] John Wick第3集單槍匹馬殺出紐約？","createTime":"2018-05-07T12:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T05:37:33.000Z","uid":75050,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"9092620cec6fb2bef8182d109cf66aeb87242992","tid":656722,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T12:48:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkgolden.com/articles/article.aspx?id=26477&amp;catid=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgolden.com%2Farticles%2Farticle.aspx%3Fid%3D26477%26catid%3D21&d=smGWapF1gBtCZO2bCLKnjozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=d08455ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkgolden.com/articles/article.aspx?id=26477&amp;catid=21</a><br />\n<br />\nJohn Wick第3集單槍匹馬殺出紐約？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/204727_f388503eb9045d24570d848856f9793f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F204727_f388503eb9045d24570d848856f9793f.jpg&h=e483c2a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《殺神John Wick 3》官方介紹出爐，新作緊接住第2集結局，主角John Wick於刺客酒店Continental內破戒射殺Santino D'Antonio，有High Table成員出1400萬美元高價「買起」John Wick，引來全球殺手追捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJohn Wick原本應該被處決，但酒店話事人Winston給予John Wick一個鐘寬限期，隨後酒店就會撤銷其會員資格及禁止任何支援服務，而John必須利用一個鐘嘅空檔殺出紐約市。<span style=\"color: red;\">Lonnie Rashid Lynn Jr.、Ruby Rose</span>及Laurence Fishburne將回歸，真田廣之首度參演《殺神John Wick》系列。電影定於2019年5月17日上映。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源:<a href=\"http://CBR.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FCBR.com&d=smGWapF1gBtCZO2bCLKnjozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=80420100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">CBR.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cbr.com/john-wick-3-synopsis/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbr.com%2Fjohn-wick-3-synopsis%2F&d=smGWapF1gBtCZO2bCLKnjozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=420c50fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cbr.com/john-wick-3-synopsis/</a>"},{"pid":"ac7d3c2597748